{"tid":1616282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10.1睇直播見到好多小朋友唔識爆玻璃，不如等我講解吓","createTime":"2019-10-03T10:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T11:55:38.000Z","uid":93273,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b21dc5a255b48224afddccafdf7e0eef02e4aa83","tid":1616282,"uid":93273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:53:49.000Z","msg":"10.1嗰時我喺屋企睇緊長沙灣政府合署嗰邊嘅直播，見到好多黑衫好辛苦咁爆玻璃，起勢咁車都車唔爆。<br />\n<br />\n小妹當然反對暴力啦，但係又諗到，如果火燭又或者坐巴士車禍要逃生，玻璃都唔識爆點算？所以就想簡單講吓點樣有效地爆玻璃。<br />\n<br />\n1. 要有合適工具，大家搭巴士嗰時都會見到一個紅色嘅鍋仔，其實就係專門爆玻璃用嘅。當然啦，咁如果平時屋企火燭點算呢？總唔可以喺巴士拎番屋企啦，咁多老閉。其實好多地方都有得賣玻璃擊破器，買番個喺屋企多個保障呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAjhs5L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAjhs5L.jpg&h=249a27c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 要敲正確位置。如果你敲正中間，就算俾把專用鎚仔你都有排搞，正確方法係敲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塊玻璃嘅四邊，尤其近角位</span>。呢個同玻璃嘅covalent bond structure有關，不過大家知點做就得。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以好好學吓點樣爆玻璃，可以喺緊急關頭救你一命！"},{"pid":"3ca4c63dd4a720dcf8fd6da9fffb0ca7ff4bd223","tid":1616282,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"點用?一野隊落塊玻璃就得?"},{"pid":"c80987bf0ee075699aaefcbf6a31e4cc307ba5b5","tid":1616282,"uid":324544,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:56:07.000Z","msg":"推。。。 又長知識啦<br />\n😎😎😎😎😎😎"},{"pid":"dfdde084d52320e944032e2bdf7ee768dd87aa5e","tid":1616282,"uid":324544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ca4c63dd4a720dcf8fd6da9fffb0ca7ff4bd223","tid":1616282,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:55:42.000Z","msg":"點用?一野隊落塊玻璃就得?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:57:01.000Z","msg":"敲四邊角呀"},{"pid":"2bc12d90d284aa6c397536e287cc8a0a726d872b","tid":1616282,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:00:22.000Z","msg":"請問呢個叫咩魔法?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616275</a>"},{"pid":"745a76f05f92b0a44bec3b8f64f1b68538d92255","tid":1616282,"uid":128705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:01:04.000Z","msg":"我發現好多人都唔識基本求生術<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad481f73f8eef8124ee513502363a9877ce0c293","tid":1616282,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"易爆程度：角 &gt; 邊 &gt; 中<br />\n（所以飛機窗係圓邊，順帶一提）"},{"pid":"2106b301f5badda6e5374c3392c647b7e05bce96","tid":1616282,"uid":219722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:11:40.000Z","msg":"強化玻璃最脆弱係4角<br />\n試過同裝修師傅拎起件7尺高玻璃<br />\n一下唔為意有一隻角撞左落磁磚地板 , 成件粉碎喺面前 , 好L彩低頭如果唔係入哂眼。<br />\n<br />\n但如果遇到夾膠玻璃就放棄啦 , 南亞泥頭佬用十磅鎚都打到氣喘先會離框成塊痴住跌落嚟"},{"pid":"369ad18a9c1d8c7b7a444f6c9e742901c9640fb4","tid":1616282,"uid":297672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"同埋，起擊破車窗逃生時，如果有眼罩同防割手套，就會安全好多。逃生時，請俾其他乘客有心理準備，以免玻璃入眼。"},{"pid":"befa5fb6d70e60e3ff9b5e3232a857648cbf4940","tid":1616282,"uid":1815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"救命逃生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4bd32773231674b901d005a4cd731c3157deb73","tid":1616282,"uid":89161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e191284af7930cd213a48b0028c828fbd659575a","tid":1616282,"uid":190807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad481f73f8eef8124ee513502363a9877ce0c293","tid":1616282,"uid":297672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"易爆程度：角 &gt; 邊 &gt; 中<br />\n（所以飛機窗係圓邊，順帶一提）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T11:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起全球第一架噴射式民航客機de Havilland Comet就係因為方形窗而係空中解體"},{"pid":"5f2e9591ea1019ef79